{"word":"G862 - ἄφθαρτος - áphthartos - af'-thar-tos - Not corruptible","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄφθαρτος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">áphthartos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">af'-thar-tos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Not corruptible</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"அழிவில்லாத, அழியாத - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"uncorrupted, not liable to corruption or decay, imperishable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G5351 - φθείρω - phtheírō - fthi'-ro/5351\">G5351</a>; <i>undecaying</i> (in essence or continuance): - not (in-, un-) corruptible, immortal.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1311/1311\">G1311</a>, <a href=\"#/G1312/1312\">G1312</a>, <a href=\"#/G2704/2704\">G2704</a>, <a href=\"#/G5256/5256\">G5256</a>, <a href=\"#/G5349/5349\">G5349</a>, <a href=\"#/G5351/5351\">G5351</a>, <a href=\"#/G861/861\">G861</a>, <a href=\"#/G862/862\">G862</a>, <a href=\"#/G90/90\">G90</a>"}]}